    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Bulk Trash Pickup</h2>
      <div class="bg-gov-blue-light rounded-xl p-5 mb-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-navy">Each residential unit is allotted <strong>one free bulk pickup per fiscal year</strong>. Additional pickups beyond the free annual pickup require a fee in accordance with the City's fee schedule, paid prior to pickup.</p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        To schedule your bulk pickup, call <a href="tel:+14102974259" class="text-gov-blue font-semibold hover:underline">(410) 297-4259</a> or fill out the bulk request form and email it to <a href="mailto:dpw@aberdeenmd.gov" class="text-gov-blue font-semibold hover:underline">dpw@aberdeenmd.gov</a>.
      </p>
      <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl p-5 mb-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-amber-800 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Important</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-800">Do <strong>NOT</strong> place items out for pickup until you have received confirmation from the Environmental Department regarding your scheduled date.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">What We Accept</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">For large appliances such as washers, dryers, refrigerators, and other white goods, special handling may be required. Contact the Environmental Division for guidance.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-green-700 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            Accepted Items
          </h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-1">
            <li>Furniture (sofas, beds, chairs)</li>
            <li>Mattresses</li>
            <li>Large appliances</li>
            <li>Electronics</li>
            <li>Yard waste (bundled)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-red-600 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            Not Accepted
          </h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-1">
            <li>Hazardous materials</li>
            <li>Paint &amp; chemicals</li>
            <li>Construction debris</li>
            <li>Tires</li>
            <li>Loose dirt or gravel</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

